Introducing the Michael Scott Coin - A Dundie-Worthy Cryptocurrency!

Attention, loyal fans of the World's Best Boss,

I have some groundbreaking news that will make your paper-loving hearts skip a beat! Brace yourselves, because I'm thrilled to announce the official public mint of the Michael Scott Coin – a cryptocurrency that will revolutionize the Dunder Mifflin financial game!
